shared
Class NetUtils

java.lang.Object
  shared.NetUtils

public class NetUtils
extends java.lang.Object

A utility class used for communication between a ClientHandler and a GuestBookClient. The class defines the types of communication headers which can be sent between ClientHandler and GuestBookClient, and provides methods for sending and receiving requests and responses.
